headline.main: MIDYEAR, 64 TO 1, FIRST AT TROPICAL; Scores by Half Length Over Pipe of Peace -- The Eagle, 5-2 Choice, Runs Last

results.snippet: CORAL GABLES, Fla., Dec. 10 (UP) -- P. Studioso's Midyear, a 64-to-1 item in the wagering, dashed through the stretch at Tropical Park today to score a half-length triumph in the Propeller Club purse.

headline.main: VAN CROSBY BEATS IS WAS IN FLORIDA; Wins by Length and Quarter in Dash at Tropical After 15-Month Racing Lay-Off

results.snippet: CORAL GABLES, Fla., Dec. 21 (AP) -- The Duntreath Farm's Van Crosby, inactive for fifteen months, staged an impressive comeback at Tropical Park today as he turned back seven seasoned opponents in the seventh and best race of the chilly afternoon.

headline.main: Precious Stone Nips Scimitar at Tropical; HANDICAP IS TAKEN BY PRECIOUS STONE

results.snippet: CORAL GABLES, Fla., Dec. 25 -- Harvey C. Fruehauf's Precious Stone took the lead an eighth of a mile from home and hung on to win the $11,475 Christmas Handicap at Tropical Park today before 13,901 shivering fans.
